text: Oliwer Magnusson (born 3 June 2000) is a Swedish freestyle skier who competes internationally. He competed in the 2017 FIS Freestyle World Ski Championships, and in the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Sweden Category:Freestyle skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics
